title_bed_bats_review: Rental unit in Bashundhara · 3 bedrooms · 3 beds · 3 baths
listing_description: We've been hosting the guests in our serviced apartment for like 4 years. Its located in Bashundhara, which is known for its calmness & security. Its located just 5 km away from Airport and its 10 mins journey by car. Our apartment has 2 ac bedrooms with attach baths & 1 non ac bedroom with non attach bath. Its fully furnished with all kinds of amenity, including kitchen utilities. The building is equipped with generator & lift service. Surrounding areas are also quiet & peaceful.
